            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                <div class="space2-content">
                  <p>Tennis, Volleyball, Theater (especially comedy), historical museums, bars, concerts and festivals, drawings, cinema, series.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row">
            <div class="space2">
              <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                <div class="space2-title">
                  <p><strong>What about Bastien?</strong></p>
                </div>
